---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Francesc Català-Moll">
  <article class="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Left: Text -->
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
              About Me
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Hi! I'm Francesc, a bioinformatics researcher passionate about unraveling the complexities of the microbiome and its role in human health.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              I combine computational biology, data science, and statistical modeling to understand how microbial communities influence immune responses and disease progression.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Profile Image Placeholder -->
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
            <div class="w-80 h-80 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/5 border-4 border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl">
              <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-primary/40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Background & Journey -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">
          My Journey
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            My fascination with biology and computation began during my undergraduate studies, where I discovered the power of data-driven approaches to answer fundamental questions about life. This led me to pursue specialized training in bioinformatics and computational genomics.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg">
            Over the past several years, I've focused on microbiome research—investigating how trillions of microorganisms living in and on our bodies influence health, disease, and therapeutic outcomes. My work bridges wet-lab biology and computational analysis, allowing me to design experiments, generate high-throughput sequencing data, and develop analytical pipelines to extract meaningful insights.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg">
            I'm particularly interested in the intersection of the microbiome with immunology and epigenetics, exploring how microbial communities shape immune cell behavior and gene regulation in health and disease contexts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Research Interests -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-primary/5">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">
          Research Interests
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-2">
                  Microbiome & Immunity
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Exploring how microbial communities modulate immune responses, inflammation, and host defense mechanisms in various disease contexts.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-2">
                  Data Analysis & Methods
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Developing robust computational methods and statistical frameworks for analyzing high-dimensional microbiome and multi-omics datasets.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-2">
                  Epigenetics & Gene Regulation
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Investigating how environmental factors and microbial signals shape epigenetic landscapes and influence gene expression patterns.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 4 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-slate-200 hover:border-primary transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-2">
                  Translational Research
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                  Bridging basic research and clinical applications to develop microbiome-based biomarkers and therapeutic interventions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills & Expertise -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">
          Skills & Expertise
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Computational Skills -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9 3L5 6.99h3V14h2V6.99h3L9 3zm7 14.01V10h-2v7.01h-3L15 21l4-3.99h-3z"/>
              </svg>
              Computational
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>R & Bioconductor ecosystem</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Python for data science</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Statistical modeling & ML</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>High-performance computing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Pipeline development (Snakemake, Nextflow)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Biological Skills -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M19.5 12c0-1.67-.67-3.17-1.76-4.24l-1.42 1.42C17.15 9.99 17.5 10.95 17.5 12s-.35 2.01-1.18 2.82l1.42 1.42C18.83 15.17 19.5 13.67 19.5 12zM15 12c0 .83-.33 1.58-.88 2.12l1.42 1.42C16.4 14.68 17 13.4 17 12s-.6-2.68-1.46-3.54l-1.42 1.42c.55.54.88 1.29.88 2.12zM12 1C9.34 1 7.09 2.79 6.35 5.27L3.61 4.42C2.68 4.14 1.76 4.79 1.5 5.73L1.03 7.67C.77 8.61 1.43 9.53 2.36 9.81l2.99.91C5.13 11.43 5 12.2 5 13v8c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h10c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-8c0-.8-.13-1.57-.35-2.28l2.99-.91c.93-.28 1.59-1.2 1.33-2.14l-.47-1.94c-.26-.94-1.18-1.59-2.11-1.31l-2.74.85C16.91 2.79 14.66 1 12 1zm0 2c1.66 0 3 1.34 3 3s-1.34 3-3 3-3-1.34-3-3 1.34-3 3-3z"/>
              </svg>
              Biological
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>16S rRNA & shotgun metagenomics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>RNA-seq & transcriptomics</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Epigenomics (ChIP-seq, ATAC-seq)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Multi-omics integration</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Experimental design</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Other Skills -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-handwritten font-medium text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/>
              </svg>
              Communication
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Scientific writing & publishing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Data visualization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Presentation & teaching</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Collaborative research</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary mt-1">•</span>
                <span>Open science & reproducibility</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Beyond Research -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-primary/5">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">
          Beyond Research
        </h2>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-200">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            When I'm not analyzing sequencing data or writing code, you'll find me exploring new hiking trails, experimenting with sourdough fermentation (the best kind of microbiology outside the lab!), or diving into the latest science fiction novels.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I'm passionate about science communication and making complex biological concepts accessible to broader audiences. I believe that sharing our research journey—including the challenges and failures—is essential for inspiring the next generation of scientists.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            I'm also committed to open science practices, reproducible research, and contributing to the scientific community through open-source software development and data sharing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Let's Connect
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          I'm always interested in collaborative opportunities, discussing research ideas, or chatting about bioinformatics and data science.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            Get in touch
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/publications"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-900 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200"
          >
            View publications
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
